reviewText: This 3-disc set is a 3-in-1 reissue of the 2002 Halloween dvd, the 2003 Christmas one, and to love a patty from 2008. Sadly the valentine episode from 2000 isn't in here nor did it get its own dvd. If you don't wanna browse the season sets for these, here's a good set to look in, in a rush. Both of the stop-motion holiday specials are in a holiday collection of their own, and sold separately. I'm ready... For the holidays!
good movie for the little one
Great gift and very pleased with everything
